title: The Bermuda Triangle (1979).avi
description:
The Bermuda Triangle (1979)

A sensationalistic look at a number of incidents in the so-called "Devil&#039;s Triangle", based on the Charles Berlitz book.  Produced by Sunn Classics Films.

As I am not in the business of spreading known false information, a more rational approach to the Bermuda Triangle mystery can be found here: http://skepdic.com/bermuda.html

Fun film to watch though. :)
